<br>
 &quot;I don't see why I even care about you people. But bless the world you are all around sometimes.&quot;<br>
<br>
 Dawn smiled lightly and stood, leaving her outlook of Olympus.<br>
 <p>Pyschotic injustice
Mommy made me this way
Evil and hungry
I'm just a craving soul
Craving for your blood and death; M'Dear
