Deciding that writing notes was too difficult, she spoke with her mind to him.<br>
<br>
~Alot is going on with the Olympians. The Furies are on a strike so to speak. Poseidon is not on many people's good list lately.~ <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#003366><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/umojotheminotaur.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Mojo the Minotaur</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 16<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(6/7/01 4:49 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=41.topic&index=17>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Mojo's response</span><hr size=1> ::With a bit of suprise in his voice as well as curiosity::<br>
<br>
&quot;On strike?  Can you guys actually do that?  Geez things just seem to get stranger and stranger around here.&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#336699><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/utheerinyes.showPublicProfile?language=EN>The Erinyes</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 59<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(6/7/01 5:10 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=41.topic&index=18>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> With a nod</span><hr size=1> She smiled and nodded her head to the question.<br>
<br>
~It is odd, however there are times when it is needed. We still tend to our sacred duties that the mortals are in some need of, but we have ceased for the time to tend to the Gods desires. . . ~<br>
<br>
Her thoughts were then brought to a mumble. . <br>
~Well. . . Megaera and I have. Alecto has been trying to find other ways.~<br>
<br>
She then rolled her eyes.<br>
<br>
~I am having a feast at the temple to try and once again bring Olympus to a peace. Although my anger towards Poseidon at this moment is strong, I wish peace among the Family.~<br>
<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#003366><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/umojotheminotaur.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Mojo the Minotaur</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 17<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(6/7/01 9:50 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=41.topic&index=19>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> With a smile...</span><hr size=1> &quot;So the Olympians are at eachother throats again?  What else is new.  They can be nice when they need to...otherwise they bicker bicker bicker.  And you are going to try and make peace at your feast?  May good fortune be with you, for you will need it.  But I look foward to it.  I seriously doubt you hear this often but, I actually enjoy your company.&quot;<br>
<br>
::He gives a grin and begins looking at the sky:: <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#336699><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/utheerinyes.showPublicProfile?language=EN>The Erinyes</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 60<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(6/8/01 1:32 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=41.topic&index=20>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Smile. . .</span><hr size=1> She smiled hearing this. . . it had been a very long time since she had heard that. The only people who ever enjoyed her company were her sisters as well as the Titans did. Hera was of course acceptable, but she had so many other things to attend to.<br>
<br>
~Have you heard of Hera's her child? She recently had a baby girl. The Feast is actually a surprise baby shower thing.~ She smiled.<br>
<br>
~Don't tell anyone though.~<br>
<br>
She smiled looking towards him.<br>
<br>
~By the way. . . I enjoy your company as well.~ <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page  <b>1</b> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showMessageRange?topicID=41.topic&start=21&stop=21>2</a> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showPrevMessage?topicID=41.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showNextMessage?topicID=41.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=41.topic&index=20><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/blueMoon/addReply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.emailToFriend?topicID=41.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.threadControl?topicID=41.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/blueMoon/deleteThread.jpg border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=41.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/subscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to receive email notification of replies"> Click to receive email notification of replies</a> <br>  <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=41.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/unsubscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to stop receiving email notification of replies"> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies</a> <br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><t